What's wrong with you, Soo-bin?

787
00:56:19,667 --> 00:56:21,086
You need to focus.

788
00:56:22,962 --> 00:56:24,881
Soo-bin, do you feel sick?

789
00:56:30,553 --> 00:56:33,098
I'm sorry, but may I go
to the nurse's office?

790
00:56:33,181 --> 00:56:35,475
The nurse's office? Let's go.

791
00:56:39,854 --> 00:56:41,773
-Soo-bin. Oh, no.
-Oh, my god.

792
00:56:41,981 --> 00:56:44,859
Quiet. This is a test. Stay in your seats.

793
00:56:45,443 --> 00:56:47,403
-Soo-bin?
-I'll carry her.

794
00:57:11,678 --> 00:57:12,679
Get back to the test.

795
00:57:18,643 --> 00:57:20,145
I'll be right back.

796
00:57:22,313 --> 00:57:24,399
Okay, quiet. Focus on the test.

797
00:57:28,194 --> 00:57:29,529
My test...

798
00:57:29,612 --> 00:57:31,948
What about her test?
She probably didn't finish.

799
00:57:32,031 --> 00:57:34,284
I know. We still have 20 minutes left.

800
00:57:36,327 --> 00:57:38,538
Can she take the test
in the nurse's office?

801
00:57:38,621 --> 00:57:39,789
I heard that was allowed.

802
00:57:39,873 --> 00:57:42,375
That will work. I'll get her test papers.

803
00:57:42,459 --> 00:57:44,002
-Go ahead.
-Okay.

804
00:57:47,964 --> 00:57:49,966
Don't worry. You'll feel better
if you take medicine.

805
00:57:50,049 --> 00:57:51,384
You can take the test.

806
00:57:52,093 --> 00:57:54,679
Jun-u's back is warm.

807
00:57:55,013 --> 00:57:57,599
I didn't think it would be, but it's warm.

808
00:58:06,065 --> 00:58:08,234
Ma'am. Soo-bin.

809
00:58:08,318 --> 00:58:09,360
What's wrong?

810
00:58:12,197 --> 00:58:13,281
Do you feel sick?

811
00:58:13,364 --> 00:58:16,326
Let's see.

812
00:58:16,784 --> 00:58:18,203
Hold on.

813
00:58:20,914 --> 00:58:23,041
It looks like acute stomach cramps.

814
00:58:23,416 --> 00:58:24,542
Hold on.

815
00:58:29,297 --> 00:58:30,840
Jun-u, here's your test.

816
00:58:32,383 --> 00:58:33,384
I'm fine.

817
00:58:33,468 --> 00:58:35,053
You're a student too.

818
00:59:13,925 --> 00:59:15,176
Did you finish?

819
00:59:16,678 --> 00:59:17,971
Jun-u.

820
00:59:18,805 --> 00:59:20,223
Soo-bin.

821
00:59:22,058 --> 00:59:25,103
I'll turn them in
to the math teacher, so wait here.

822
00:59:50,461 --> 00:59:51,796
Are you feeling better now?

823
00:59:54,299 --> 00:59:56,467
Yes. Thanks.

824
00:59:56,634 --> 00:59:59,262
I'm sorry you lost time for the test
because of me.

825
00:59:59,345 --> 01:00:00,346
Sorry.

826
01:00:00,888 --> 01:00:02,515
It's okay.

827
01:00:02,974 --> 01:00:05,059
I had no idea how to solve
the problems in the back anyway.

828
01:00:12,650 --> 01:00:14,652
You can go now. I can stay by myself.

829
01:00:15,111 --> 01:00:16,446
I will once the nurse gets back.

830
01:00:18,489 --> 01:00:19,782
Am I making you uncomfortable?

831
01:00:23,286 --> 01:00:24,495
I'll go then.

832
01:00:39,260 --> 01:00:40,887
Hey. Your hand.

833
01:00:44,557 --> 01:00:45,850
Was it from earlier?

834
01:00:46,851 --> 01:00:47,769
I didn't know.

835
01:00:47,852 --> 01:00:51,022
You should have the nurse treat it.

836
01:00:51,189 --> 01:00:52,357
It may get infected.

837
01:00:54,817 --> 01:00:55,985
It's okay.

838
01:00:57,153 --> 01:00:58,321
Get it treated.

839
01:01:02,283 --> 01:01:03,326
Maybe I should.

840
01:01:22,345 --> 01:01:23,179
Hey.

841
01:01:24,597 --> 01:01:26,474
About what I said the other day.

842
01:01:27,725 --> 01:01:28,768
Which part?

843
01:01:30,186 --> 01:01:31,396
When Bumbi...

844
01:01:32,397 --> 01:01:35,441
When your bike broke. I mean...

845
01:01:35,900 --> 01:01:38,861
What I said right before it broke.

846
01:01:40,238 --> 01:01:41,864
Please forget it.

847
01:01:41,948 --> 01:01:42,949
Me too.

848
01:01:44,200 --> 01:01:45,201
What?

849
01:01:45,660 --> 01:01:47,704
I was going to say this then too.

850
01:01:48,121 --> 01:01:49,247
Exactly.

851
01:01:50,456 --> 01:01:52,834
I know what you're about to say.

852
01:02:00,216 --> 01:02:01,175
What?

853
01:02:01,259 --> 01:02:02,969
I wanted to get some water.

854
01:02:03,052 --> 01:02:04,721
-I'll get it.
-No,

855
01:02:04,804 --> 01:02:05,805
it's okay.

856
01:02:10,309 --> 01:02:14,355
So... That is...

857
01:02:14,814 --> 01:02:16,858
Don't feel bad...

858
01:02:17,775 --> 01:02:22,238
Just... forget... everything...

859
01:02:23,322 --> 01:02:24,532
I like you.

860
01:02:37,587 --> 01:02:40,047
I like you too.

861
01:02:53,478 --> 01:02:54,687
I like you.

862
01:03:14,582 --> 01:03:17,376
Mr. Oh, I think I've seen that boy
somewhere before.

863
01:03:17,460 --> 01:03:19,462
-He was forced to transfer--
-It was just a regular one.

864
01:03:19,545 --> 01:03:21,589
Why did he carry you earlier?
Why does he keep coming up?

865
01:03:21,672 --> 01:03:23,216
Don't even go anywhere near him.

866
01:03:23,299 --> 01:03:25,176
The answer is number two.

867
01:03:25,259 --> 01:03:27,929
It's just one question.
Don't worry so much.

868
01:03:28,012 --> 01:03:29,514
What do you know?

869
01:03:29,597 --> 01:03:31,349
I've been thinking it over,

870
01:03:31,432 --> 01:03:33,851
and I guess I'll accept you. Let's go out.

871
01:03:34,852 --> 01:03:36,103
Rock-paper-scissors!

872
01:03:37,522 --> 01:03:40,817
Soo-bin, you're like a pea. A tiny pea.

873
01:03:41,651 --> 01:03:42,568
Soo-bin.

874
01:03:46,989 --> 01:03:48,491
Hello, I'm Choe Jun-u.

875
01:03:56,040 --> 01:03:58,167
Subtitle translation by Wayne Ryu

